Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這個國家的王子是個無人能及的咖哩狂熱者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但是最近做得有點過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,強行要求國民給他做美味的咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他吃了之後如果不滿意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就會讓烹飪的人按難吃程度徵收5倍、10倍、20倍的稅金
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,因為這個 人們…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.34,0:11:35.55,zs,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\bord0\shad0\c&H694F36&\b1\pos(508.5,918)\2a&HFF&}{\k8}但{\k8}是{\k8}因{\k8}為{\k8}這{\k8}個{\k8} {\k8}人{\k8}們{\k8}…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.09,0:11:35.55,zs,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\bord0\shad0\c&H694F36&\b1\pos(1690.5,190.5)}{\pos(1702.5,190.5)}{\t(2000,2000,\c&HFFFFFF&)}{\t(2100,2100,\c&H694F36&)}{\t(2190,2190,\c&HFFFFFF&)}{\t(2270,2270,\c&H694F36&)}逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:35.18,zs,,0,0,0,,{\fscx62\fscy55\bord0\shad0\c&H694F36&\b1\pos(1732.5,213)}{\p1}m -76.5 -54 l 82.5 -54 b 90 -54 99 -46.5 99 -37.5 l 99 45 b 99 52.5 90 61.5 82.5 61.5 l -76.5 61.5 b -85.5 61.5 -93 52.5 -93 45 l -93 -37.5 b -93 -46.5 -85.5 -54 -76.5 -54{\p0}
